{"tid":1760083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用一個論述就能取得所有立會議席及功能組別議席","createTime":"2019-11-28T03:48:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T04:57:42.000Z","uid":84408,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1cce819dd0cb1a58aace15eb88ca609103972e47","tid":1760083,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:48:54.000Z","msg":"無錯 就係講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">當民主派取得大勝後 <br />\n社會相對回復平靜</span></span><br />\n呢個係一個不爭事實黎<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而大部份人為咗和平<br />\n都會轉投返民主派 <br />\n因為好多人係勝利球迷<br />\n甚至係利益取向<br />\n<br />\n以此為論述 必定取得一定數量選票<br />\n即是相反論述為<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果建制派取得大勝<br />\n社會會重回動盪之中<br />\n因為佢地係根源 係始作俑者</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同樣 功能組別如商界等如果非民主派<br />\n社會同樣會重回動盪<br />\n零售工商將會繼續攬炒<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">劍指建制派</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以運動要持續並非易事<br />\n如果我地未能成功集氣重回運動<br />\n則需要改變模式及論述<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲黎講<br />\n <span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一係比我地贏 <br />\n一係攬炒<br />\n就算功能組別有任何一個建制派<br />\n社會都會繼續不穩定<br />\n攬炒將會繼續</span></span><br />\n群眾想揀邊樣? 自己決定啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b447110fa17114c960e0afae01b57d978b16eb","tid":1760083,"uid":84408,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:51:18.000Z","msg":"經濟大春袋將會以工會模式呈現<br />\n假若建制大勝<br />\n將會民不聊生<br />\n老人院執笠<br />\n經濟將會嚴重下行<br />\n出現大飢荒"},{"pid":"c8eb6d448f141437d783adffbe51e7fc92be664f","tid":1760083,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:54:56.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"691d2bbf1b837c78c698c0c99973130dab6fec7a","tid":1760083,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:58:50.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f8b80df31af7521ced86f67579b6743f4f3f17","tid":1760083,"uid":117792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:59:54.000Z","msg":"認同 但小心冇左道火"},{"pid":"db54cc1963f8b9c5a761b5e9009720338fc87ef5","tid":1760083,"uid":84408,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a1f8b80df31af7521ced86f67579b6743f4f3f17","tid":1760083,"uid":117792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:59:54.000Z","msg":"認同 但小心冇左道火"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:01:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8ebdc16d754b35f7a83a144dd21d815236a847","tid":1760083,"uid":290694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:01:27.000Z","msg":"眼見連登一邊話立法會無可能過半, 立法會廢, 無用。我明。<br />\n<br />\n但係老豆豆講真係會有和理非, 會想係個制度裡面盡可能改變令普遍市民既聲音可以主導個政府。<br />\n<br />\n我亦都知好大部分人係堅信五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n首先係要政府回應、答應五大訴求先。<br />\n其中一項係真雙普選，如果做唔到依樣野，係唔可以一步到位做到從體制裡面改變香港。<br />\n但係淋病政府一直冷處理，一路拖，拖左我地半年依家先出個&lt;&lt;獨立&quot;檢討&quot;委員會&gt;&gt;。<br />\n<br />\n我個人無咁叻，我唔知道政府黎緊會點做。<br />\n我唔知個政府想拖我地幾耐。<br />\n政府唔回應、答應。我地就升級再升級。<br />\n就好似打緊一場長久而睇唔到終點既仗。<br />\n<br />\n但係立法會選舉下年黎緊，話長唔長，話短唔短，好快就到！<br />\n我地仲係到自己人屌自己人，做人都要有Plan A，Plan B。<br />\n點解仲唔可以停止爭論！<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求我地要政府俾到交代我地，缺一不可。<br />\n立法會最基本野要做好，夠資格就登記做選民。<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力，目標一致。<br />\n繼續high人權法、區議會，我睇唔到香港人出路！<br />\n區議會贏，人權法贏，然後我係幾等公民?<br />\n<br />\nD 濕9政客我地睇下就好啦!<br />\n我地係爭取緊人一出世就要有既野!!<br />\n<br />\n推下行動post好過啦!!!"},{"pid":"b8270e0de29b0c19240036f1bd57d4a38a30560b","tid":1760083,"uid":290694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:02:06.000Z","msg":"依個氣氛你確保下年一定得?"},{"pid":"223020d7122a2832913fad8121367a4c35a6118b","tid":1760083,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:36:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"817181ed7c2458b68fae628fadedd6eb47da8857","tid":1760083,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:41:04.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db851c57f8a94a38fcfb1e609a081c023193c49","tid":1760083,"uid":84408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:44:35.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6995c392ef7e50c0dcc71383b5de7c12b44f85c","tid":1760083,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:46:41.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc837bb7f40bf11676eb3cd05711403b542c994","tid":1760083,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:57:42.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}